responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "2A5B410B4184A0D7756E349A21D900AE", "His despair must be great, to ask one such as yourself for aid. Harl disdains godkin, almost as much as he disdains goblins. Have you come in good faith? Will you help to see this through?")
name: SQ_32_Sehmi_Dialog_31
